high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up to the round wooden table.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the wooden table.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk towards the sink, turn right and walk up to the other side of the round wooden table.
Slice up the apple that is on the round wooden table.
Put the large knife back on the round wooden table.
Pick up a piece of sliced apple.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the piece of sliced apple inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled piece of sliced apple and close the fridge.
Turn right and walk over to the round wooden table, then turn right and walk over to the silver bin to the left of the counter.
Put the chilled piece of sliced apple into the silver bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of sliced apple in a silver bin.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go across the room to the wall, turn to the left and go to the dining table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the table.
Go around the dining table to the other side.
Cut the apple that is on the table into pieces.
Put the knife down on the table.
Pick up a piece of the apple that is on the table.
Turn around and go to the fridge that is on the right.
Put the apple inside the fridge and close the door, remove the apple from the fridge once it is cold.
Turn to the right, go to the table, hang a right, go to the counter, hang a left and go forward to the garbage can that is on the right.
Put the apple inside the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put cold piece of apple inside the garbage can.

high_descs: Walk across the room to reach the round wooden table.
Pick up the large knife from the round wooden table.
Turn around to walk to the other side of the table.
Slice the apple on the table.
Set the knife down on the table.
Pick up a slice of apple from the table.
Turn around to walk to the fridge.
Chill the slice of apple in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn around to walk to the trash can in the left corner.
Throw the apple slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple slice in the fridge to throw it away in the trash can.
